 times the instantaneous SFRs. Our results demonstrates\nhow background quasars can be used to measure wind properties with high\nprecision.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 26 Oct 2011 19:02:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 10 Jan 2012 13:57:23 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 27 May 2012 20:19:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-30"}
