ing the advantages, disadvantages and limitations of both the\nfield extrapolation and analytic approaches, and also those of\nmagnetohydrodynamic models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 26 Oct 2011 19:57:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-30"}
