\nvariance with previous calculations using idealized equilibrium nuclear disk\nmodels. (abridged)\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Oct 2011 14:16:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 24 Dec 2012 14:44:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-30"}
